Class AccountTransactions

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.AccountTransactions

  • public class AccountTransactions
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    nathanmauch AccountTransactions is a model class that creates the array list needed for the account and spending controller. It takes the values that are passed to it from reading the customers transaction file and inserts them into an array list
